{"tid":2029630,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如何在屋企水耕","createTime":"2020-05-22T10:26:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T15:07:26.000Z","uid":37144,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ffc3f9e6a3ade8ed9b5f366b361d3d7db6a6bc4d","tid":2029630,"uid":37144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:26:34.000Z","msg":"Hello 大家好 想同大家講下喺屋企點水耕 <br />\n首先啦 點令到屋企啱種嘢要睇幾樣嘢<br />\n最重要係光 介質  同温度 同棵植物本身<br />\n<br />\n光啦 要睇夠唔夠光 要睇座向 同有冇樓遮住<br />\n向東西通常會唔太夠光 向南北就更加夠<br />\n另外 有樓係對遮住點都唔夠<br />\n同如果種屋企入面 就一定冇種出面咁夠光<br />\n但種入面蟲害 比bird食 比風吹走既問題會小D<br />\n<br />\n同埋點分辬 夠唔夠光 最重要就係睇有冇徒長<br />\n簡單D講 佢生得好快 但生得好瘦好長 咁就係徒長 唔夠光<br />\n咁點樣解決呢個問題呢 就係揾燈照佢<br />\n咁鴨記有得賣植物燈 但我種生菜 就要用50W以上先夠力<br />\n咁當然 其實普通燈都冇咩問題 但就話植物燈就再重視D喺生長開花既光譜<br />\n不過我會建議人喺屋企同冇訓著先開燈 始終好多廢熱 我成日覺得好易燒咗屋企<br />\n總之要玩就自己小心D 我自己都諗緊買唔買個滅火筒看下門口<br />\n同日睇屋企幾光再決定開幾耐燈 我諗5~10 hrs 一日都應該夠 <br />\n同埋自己唔好成日望佢 50W既燈其實好撚光 我成日覺得睇太多對眼唔好<br />\n<br />\n咁基本上解決咗呢個問題 你係燈下面種咩都得 只要佢個温度環境啱<br />\n但要點決定用泥種定水耕呢<br />\n簡單D 泥最大問題係蟲 你住到幾撚高都唔知點解會有蟲<br />\n如果你屋企完全一丁點蟲都冇 咁我覺得用泥種好過用水種<br />\n但若果有既 咁用水耕會幾好 因為D蟲好小係活水屙蛋<br />\n<br />\n好啦  咁點樣耕呢 有幾種既 <br />\n1.Wick syetem<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nosoilsolutions.com/wick-hydroponics/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nosoilsolutions.com%2Fwick-hydroponics%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSlT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=0bc359d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nosoilsolutions.com/wick-hydroponics/</a><br />\n最簡單 下面有條線吸D肥料水上去<br />\n呢種種D香料嗰類唔收成個類就會簡單D 但佢都會有位屙蛋<br />\n叫慳翻D施肥同淋水時間 同可用可用pump 慳電D<br />\n<br />\n2. DWC<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nosoilsolutions.com/deep-water-culture-hydroponics/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nosoilsolutions.com%2Fdeep-water-culture-hydroponics%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSlT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=41ffc849\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nosoilsolutions.com/deep-water-culture-hydroponics/</a><br />\n簡單D講就係一堆水 +氣pump 咁D根因為水入面夠氧氣所以會生<br />\n咁實際買個膠箱 整幾個loan 用有機棉夾住D植物芽 咁就搞掂算係幾方便<br />\n(呢D全部金魚街買到)<br />\n我自己用呢隻 A3 size 既膠箱 大約9個loan左右<br />\n<br />\n3,NFT<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nosoilsolutions.com/nutrient-film-technique-nft-hydroponics/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nosoilsolutions.com%2Fnutrient-film-technique-nft-hydroponics%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSlT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=623092ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nosoilsolutions.com/nutrient-film-technique-nft-hydroponics/</a><br />\n想種多D通常用呢種 自己睇圖啦<br />\nD人通常買水喉自己整<br />\n<br />\n仲有氣耕同 魚菜共生 同 Ebb &amp; Flow 想知再講<br />\n<br />\n咁點搞呢 睇圖 下面自己嘢 見過勿相認<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/05/22/v4fAdH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F05%2F22%2Fv4fAdH.jpg&h=311d735e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/05/22/mJlFn9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F05%2F22%2FmJlFn9.jpg&h=5a0f60a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/05/22/Om0gLZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F05%2F22%2FOm0gLZ.jpg&h=c5dc8619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/05/22/64uyI2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F05%2F22%2F64uyI2.jpg&h=8e8e6a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/05/22/8Yea5B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F05%2F22%2F8Yea5B.jpg&h=e2ddaf8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肥料水我見有人用有機肥發酵出黎<br />\n花墟好似有一間有得買個D 水耕液 <br />\n而我自己就用花寶2號  用佢個份量減1/4左右但我貪平 用花寶算啦<br />\n驚硝酸鹽過量 但好似話食之前煮熟佢問題不大<br />\n同埋要睇埋種子D温度月份啱唔啱<br />\n再玩耐D就可以諗下買埋EC計同PH計 咁應該outcome 會好D<br />\n同埋水用蒸餾水會好D 因為水喉水可能偏高ph<br />\n<br />\n有問題再問 不過我唔係 pro 講定先<br />\n同埋D菜味道一般般  叫有得食下咁 可能用其他肥會好D<br />\n丫 收成期最快通常要30-50日 比定個心理準備大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3d0857c55e0f5f7db80b2da5e4cf71bb0ca2638","tid":2029630,"uid":30084,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:30:39.000Z","msg":"但有一個夢不會死,種大麻"},{"pid":"ed276008f4f7b348952963373e5d06a8736d9101","tid":2029630,"uid":128102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f3d0857c55e0f5f7db80b2da5e4cf71bb0ca2638","tid":2029630,"uid":30084,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:30:39.000Z","msg":"但有一個夢不會死,種大麻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:02:23.000Z","msg":"呢樣真<br />\n搞咁大壇野唔自肥真係天理不容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998ea8ebf4cd0d3941d3791a90f33e9301b45cb2","tid":2029630,"uid":37144,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ed276008f4f7b348952963373e5d06a8736d9101","tid":2029630,"uid":128102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f3d0857c55e0f5f7db80b2da5e4cf71bb0ca2638","tid":2029630,"uid":30084,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:30:39.000Z","msg":"但有一個夢不會死,種大麻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:02:23.000Z","msg":"呢樣真<br />\n搞咁大壇野唔自肥真係天理不容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:14:45.000Z","msg":"我自己就no comments la <br />\n我對大麻呢件事冇乜好感 亦都唔係我開呢個post 既原意<br />\n咁不過你學咗D知識係你既 你點用就唔關我事啦<br />\n同埋講定先 香港種大麻一定係犯法既 帶定頭盔先<br />\n<br />\n同埋老實講 一個箱 一盞燈 一個pump 一張生化棉(上面打錯咗做有機棉)<br />\n唔係D咩大嘢 $300內一定搞得掂<br />\nD人成日話發展本土農業 咁咪當share下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6d604afa419605137c7756c350c1467c8cba54","tid":2029630,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:17:00.000Z","msg":"薯仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0af52b44af2544bb49e8ced11e55b4cfe5c58f","tid":2029630,"uid":37144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb6d604afa419605137c7756c350c1467c8cba54","tid":2029630,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:17:00.000Z","msg":"薯仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:22:02.000Z","msg":"呢個得既 但好似用氣耕多<br />\n我嗰D就生菜同水菜黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ce93a5f0347d21bbc35812730ee1a296717011","tid":2029630,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:22:43.000Z","msg":"發芽菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3829dd25698d1aad0b1ebcdd86542bccc10dc3","tid":2029630,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:26:01.000Z","msg":"必推！"},{"pid":"1f8baf2ab1db6f984d90598703126596c6617e26","tid":2029630,"uid":37144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5ce93a5f0347d21bbc35812730ee1a296717011","tid":2029630,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:22:43.000Z","msg":"發芽菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:29:00.000Z","msg":"呢個最快 6日搞掂 但冇咩挑戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a381af4c6e202fde51d60983bb1e80acc1b08f","tid":2029630,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:53:52.000Z","msg":"好多字<br />\n好快咁睇哂<br />\n<br />\n我住嘅地方有陽光直射<br />\n可以曬太陽曬黑嗰隻<br />\n<br />\n我有試過放植物<br />\n問題係真係會引黎好多好多蚊蟲<br />\n雀好可愛都好小事<br />\n<br />\n但係有啲細隻蟲仔 蚊仔 之後就會有蜘蛛<br />\n非食用植物我會噴植物用殺蟲水<br />\n<br />\n但係去到呢個問題<br />\n我就唔敢種食物了<br />\n我驚毒死自己 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點搞好"},{"pid":"0d2590af015417c3d97488a545db0f13e094320f","tid":2029630,"uid":37144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35a381af4c6e202fde51d60983bb1e80acc1b08f","tid":2029630,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:53:52.000Z","msg":"好多字<br />\n好快咁睇哂<br />\n<br />\n我住嘅地方有陽光直射<br />\n可以曬太陽曬黑嗰隻<br />\n<br />\n我有試過放植物<br />\n問題係真係會引黎好多好多蚊蟲<br />\n雀好可愛都好小事<br />\n<br />\n但係有啲細隻蟲仔 蚊仔 之後就會有蜘蛛<br />\n非食用植物我會噴植物用殺蟲水<br />\n<br />\n但係去到呢個問題<br />\n我就唔敢種食物了<br />\n我驚毒死自己 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點搞好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:15:41.000Z","msg":"我都試過種辣椒  比D蚜蟲咬 用苦楝油唔得 馬拉松(唔好亂用)又唔得 最後日日攞牙刷刷  之後頂唔順由佢 最後棵嘢死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都好想有靚光 D野種出黎唔同D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食既聽講要試 有D係好奇怪 唔會有太多蟲咬 試下皇帝菜 OR 莧菜(好似係)  種之前消毒下D泥先 太陽照下佢 ,揾爐焗 whatever啦 又或者起個防蟲窗花 可能會好小小<br />\n或者真係試下水耕 可能會好小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd891887963eb4ab4939932a774bc0fb0905eae","tid":2029630,"uid":309192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3d0857c55e0f5f7db80b2da5e4cf71bb0ca2638","tid":2029630,"uid":30084,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:30:39.000Z","msg":"但有一個夢不會死,種大麻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:17:40.000Z","msg":"專業技術黎嫁你估咁易呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n種大麻好撚食電<br />\n好易人查到"},{"pid":"ec79686641093d726b3bf10795f910ed838d6802","tid":2029630,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d2590af015417c3d97488a545db0f13e094320f","tid":2029630,"uid":37144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35a381af4c6e202fde51d60983bb1e80acc1b08f","tid":2029630,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:53:52.000Z","msg":"好多字<br />\n好快咁睇哂<br />\n<br />\n我住嘅地方有陽光直射<br />\n可以曬太陽曬黑嗰隻<br />\n<br />\n我有試過放植物<br />\n問題係真係會引黎好多好多蚊蟲<br />\n雀好可愛都好小事<br />\n<br />\n但係有啲細隻蟲仔 蚊仔 之後就會有蜘蛛<br />\n非食用植物我會噴植物用殺蟲水<br />\n<br />\n但係去到呢個問題<br />\n我就唔敢種食物了<br />\n我驚毒死自己 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點搞好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:15:41.000Z","msg":"我都試過種辣椒  比D蚜蟲咬 用苦楝油唔得 馬拉松(唔好亂用)又唔得 最後日日攞牙刷刷  之後頂唔順由佢 最後棵嘢死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都好想有靚光 D野種出黎唔同D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食既聽講要試 有D係好奇怪 唔會有太多蟲咬 試下皇帝菜 OR 莧菜(好似係)  種之前消毒下D泥先 太陽照下佢 ,揾爐焗 whatever啦 又或者起個防蟲窗花 可能會好小小<br />\n或者真係試下水耕 可能會好小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:22:39.000Z","msg":"我本身有好多野想種<br />\n不過上網查完<br />\n剩係蟲呢樣野已經全部無得玩<br />\n因為基本上我可以日日淋水施肥<br />\n但我無能力慢慢除蟲<br />\n啲蟲仔係好煩好煩"},{"pid":"45443ad9dce7e086af85716a4908d849bbb12419","tid":2029630,"uid":37144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2dd891887963eb4ab4939932a774bc0fb0905eae","tid":2029630,"uid":309192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3d0857c55e0f5f7db80b2da5e4cf71bb0ca2638","tid":2029630,"uid":30084,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:30:39.000Z","msg":"但有一個夢不會死,種大麻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:17:40.000Z","msg":"專業技術黎嫁你估咁易呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n種大麻好撚食電<br />\n好易人查到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:34:35.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔鐘意大麻 但我要講既係<br />\n依家用LED D電用小咗好多<br />\n當我自己盞燈 50W 每日開10個鐘<br />\n都係500W  開2日1度電 開一個月15度電<br />\n其實唔係真係好貴 算係好平tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我嗰嗰A3 size 膠箱 用2.2w pump 開足24hr, 1個月 先1584 W<br />\n2度電都唔使 其實我諗種大麻好食電應該都係舊觀念<br />\n食唔食電係睇你種幾多<br />\n不過佢陣味好臭呢樣真係冇得呃(利申 外國見人食過)"},{"pid":"501a6809f609f3ab329a1e5c7452f19c877ac9ab","tid":2029630,"uid":37144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec79686641093d726b3bf10795f910ed838d6802","tid":2029630,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d2590af015417c3d97488a545db0f13e094320f","tid":2029630,"uid":37144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote